'''Wraith Squad''' were a group of ten elite [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] [[Commando/Legends|commandos]] who were present at the [[Battle of Mandalore (pre-Naboo)|Battle of Mandalore]]. Almost all of the group were wiped out by the [[Republican Army]] forces.<ref name="BFM">{{ChallengeCite|58|Battle for Mandalore}}</ref>

